text: Funtovo-2 () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Funtovsky Selsoviet, Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 430 as of 2010. There are 11 streets. == Geography == It is located 17 km from Astrakhan, 15 km from Nachalovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Privolzhsky District, Astrakhan Oblast
title: Funtovo-2
